{
  "stem": "21626.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you can imagine what a terrible atmosphere it was for a child coming into-- when he'd just been orphaned, and just returned, and to be subjected to that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he didn't know-- they didn't know how to cope.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in those days, there was no counseling, no help given.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I'll come to that later, because there's an interesting epitaph to that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My aunt, when she came for me, I could hardly believe what I was seeing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was overwhelmed with a feel of warmth and love for her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She'd always been skinny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Everyone predicted she would never return.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But she was the sole survivor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But she stood there, and she really was skin and bones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But it was her eyes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were just like pools of incredible, deep sadness.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I-- I just wanted to hug her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I wanted to love her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I wanted to say I'll be always there for her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I did just that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I think she felt the same.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It must have been very strange, because she said goodbye to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was such a young, [LAUGHS] little kid with whom she had been exasperated so many times.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And yet suddenly, I was the strong one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I learned from her, of course, that in that camp, she didn't just bury my mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But she also buried my two cousins, Tommy and Janus.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And all three of them died after the liberation-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] --one on the 1st of May, one on the 21st of May, on his 16th birthday, and my mother on the 10th of May.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, this was that uncle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, she was a spinster, if you remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was the spinster who lived with my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
